<section id="about" class="top-margin section-gap section-spacing">
  <Divider />
  <h2 class="heading-2 mb-6 text-center">About Me</h2>
  <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
      <AboutCard
        img="/about_where.png"
        title="It Starts With Quiet Change"
        desc={`Quiet change can be the most powerful kind. I am passionate about creating systems that empower people to do their best work without demanding attention. The most impactful systems are not flashy; they are foundational, supporting people through change and making life better in lasting ways. Whether working with naval officers on operational tools, educators on reducing administrative load, or farmers adopting new technology, I am driven by the same goal: build clarity, strengthen trust, and make progress possible.`}
      />
      <AboutCard
        img="/about_what_i_do2.png"
        title="Finding the Magic in Structure"
        desc={`I have learned that structure is where the magic happens. My approach blends clarity of purpose, structured thinking, and steady experimentation, driven by a desire to help people work with confidence and focus. This mindset began in my family’s small game console shop in Malaysia, where RPG games sparked my love for progress and discovery. Studying game programming in Singapore showed me that the “magic” behind great systems comes from logic, structure, and disciplined iteration. These principles continue to guide me as I design tools that feel intuitive and supportive, even in complex environments.`}
      />
      <AboutCard
        img="/about_foundation.png"
        title="Turning Mess Into Momentum"
        desc={`Messy problems are where I do my best work. I call myself a Clarity Alchemist — someone who turns confusion into shared progress. I build digital systems that bring clarity to complex, multi stakeholder environments, balance immediate delivery with long term sustainability, and win adoption by building trust rather than forcing change. My work spans public, private, and mission driven sectors, creating tools that people may not think about every day but rely on when it matters most.`}
      />
      <AboutCard
        img="/about_out_work.png"
        title="Where Curiosity Takes Me Next"
        desc={`Curiosity keeps me moving forward. Outside of building digital systems, I bring the same mindset to personal pursuits. I run baking experiments in my kitchen, reworking traditional recipes into low carb, high protein versions. Like product management, it starts with a vision, evolves through small tests, and improves through refinement. I also strength train daily, where progressive overload reminds me that lasting change comes from steady, measurable steps.`}
      />
  </div>
</section>
